    • Method Detail

      • onDestinationReached

        void onDestinationReached()
        Notifies when the destination is reached. This method is notified on the UI thread.

        Three scenarios can be found in here:

        1. Default behavior: the navigation continues in free drive mode.
        2. To delete the previous route from the map call SKRouteManager.clearCurrentRoute()
        3. To stop entering free drive navigation call SKNavigationManager.stopNavigation()

      • onSignalNewAdviceWithInstruction

        instruction - the advice instruction necessary for text to speech engine

      • onFreeDriveUpdated

        void onFreeDriveUpdated(java.lang.String countryCode,
                      java.lang.String streetName,
                      java.lang.String referenceName,
                      SKNavigationState.SKStreetType streetType,
                      double currentSpeed,
                      double speedLimit)
        Notifies when new updates are available in free drive mode.This method is notified on the UI thread.
        Parameters:
        countryCode - the country code for the current country.
        streetName - the name of the current street.
        referenceName - reference name
        streetType - the type of the current street.
        currentSpeed - the current speed.
        speedLimit - the current speed limit

      • onVisualAdviceChanged
